{"tid":2151584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（1994）第一部香港獨立卡通上線喇","createTime":"2020-08-11T12:42:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T13:18:47.000Z","uid":211212,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"230b9defbd28833ee9d2736008c308243947e5ea","tid":2151584,"uid":211212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T12:42:52.000Z","msg":"相信80，90後睇標題都估到講緊邊一套<br />\n就係1994年機動武鬥傳G Gundam (香港於1998年播出）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8LiK77i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8LiK77i.jpg&h=a54f81f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n卡通入面，香港竟然係一個獨立國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以Neo Hong Kong 為名參與爭奪世界統治權的高達比賽，仲拎過世界冠軍統治地球（東方不敗駕駛九龍高達參加）<br />\n<br />\n套野有一半時間都係香港發生，所以有大量動畫香港場面，而入面主要武器唔係粒子炮激光劍。而係參考左香港武俠小說及電影而發展成的功夫，可見當時香港軟實力的表現。<br />\n<br />\n主角機<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j7dSxHB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj7dSxHB.jpg&h=503a47ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n東方不敗<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GWDGqWF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGWDGqWF.png&h=54f2594e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢部係「新中國」代表，唔好鬧錯<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jiq5SB8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJiq5SB8.jpg&h=5deb3dc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n條片有好詳細介紹和香港的關係<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LCD71O0AmAs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLCD71O0AmAs&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FiWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=7380a0d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LCD71O0AmAs</a><br />\n<br />\n利伸：愛国愛党，套卡通錯哂<br />\n建議小粉紅抵制，全国禁止《機動武鬥傳》及相關產品流通販售"},{"pid":"5b333db0bacbb6f8d404f66fc72eead0e3e90de8","tid":2151584,"uid":211212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T12:47:43.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e16d35928f55220ce28e34fba12d1ca3151bbe5a","tid":2151584,"uid":230594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T12:59:05.000Z","msg":"CCtai<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24ef09eaa4f7c4eb98e3be318f05ce0cf8eb1ca9","tid":2151584,"uid":53036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T13:01:05.000Z","msg":"佢有份改左首歌好好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3ud7WTUG3Q0&amp;t=25s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3ud7WTUG3Q0%26t%3D25s&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FiWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=7a4e7ee7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3ud7WTUG3Q0&amp;t=25s</a>"},{"pid":"cca815f7cf7d1dfda0518eaab013cb134e391d35","tid":2151584,"uid":211212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24ef09eaa4f7c4eb98e3be318f05ce0cf8eb1ca9","tid":2151584,"uid":53036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T13:01:05.000Z","msg":"佢有份改左首歌好好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3ud7WTUG3Q0&amp;t=25s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3ud7WTUG3Q0%26t%3D25s&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FiWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=7a4e7ee7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3ud7WTUG3Q0&amp;t=25s</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T13:08:01.000Z","msg":"呢套真係可一不可再"},{"pid":"ed5440d98dcd095e1ef26e8407eb683606728dc4","tid":2151584,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T13:15:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2e79f34d23588e8d5624940cc9ec6e6e1bb03608","tid":2151584,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T13:18:47.000Z","msg":"笨大一向都好鍾意香港野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}